OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a bright day with
OL,6,Fsunny spells and occasional showers.
OL,7,FThe showers most frequent over Moray
OL,8,Fand western Aberdeenshire, wintry on
OL,9,Fhills. Best of the sunshine for
OL,10,FAberdeen and Stonehaven. Chilly
OL,11,Fwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMost of the showers dying out
OL,14,Fthis evening with clear skies for a
OL,15,Ftime. Thickening cloud and patchy
OL,16,Flight rain then pushing in from the
OL,17,Fwest later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
