OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMainly dry with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells developing and feeling
OL,7,Fwarm in any sunshine. Winds light or
OL,8,Fmoderate from the southwest.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,11,Fand bright start on Wednesday, but
OL,12,Frain later. Mainly dry on Thursday and
OL,13,FFriday, best of the brightness on
OL,14,FThursday with the odd shower possible
OL,15,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
